<p>Ncdc is a modern and lightweight direct connect client with a friendly ncurses interface.</p>

<h2><a class='u'
name="Get_ncdc!"
>Get ncdc!</a></h2>

<dl>
<dt><a name="Latest_version"
>Latest version</a></dt>

<dd>
<p>1.19.1 (<a href="/download/ncdc-1.19.1.tar.gz">ncdc-1.19.1.tar.gz</a><b class="sig"><a href="/download/ncdc-1.19.1.tar.gz.asc">pgp</a>-<a href="/download/ncdc-1.19.1.tar.gz.sha1">sha1</a>-<a href="/download/ncdc-1.19.1.tar.gz.md5">md5</a></b> - <a href="http://dev.yorhel.nl/ncdc/changes" class="podlinkurl"
>changes</a> - <a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/ncdc/files/ncdc/" class="podlinkurl"
>mirror</a>)</p>

<p>Convenient static binaries for Linux: <a href="http://dev.yorhel.nl/download/ncdc-linux-x86_64-1.19.1-3-g8e3a7.tar.gz" class="podlinkurl"
>64-bit</a> - <a href="http://dev.yorhel.nl/download/ncdc-linux-i486-1.19.1-3-g8e3a7.tar.gz" class="podlinkurl"
>32-bit</a> - <a href="http://dev.yorhel.nl/download/ncdc-linux-arm-1.19.1-3-g8e3a7.tar.gz" class="podlinkurl"
