Check the <a href="http://dev.yorhel.nl/ncdc/install" class="podlinkurl"
>installation instructions</a> for more info.</p>

<dt><a name="Development_version"
>Development version</a></dt>

<dd>
<p>The latest development version is available from git and can be cloned using <code>git clone git://g.blicky.net/ncdc.git</code>.
The repository is available for <a href="http://g.blicky.net/ncdc.git/" class="podlinkurl"
>online browsing</a>.</p>

<dt><a name="Requirements"
>Requirements</a></dt>

<dd>
<p>The following libraries are required: ncurses,
zlib,
bzip2,
sqlite3,
glib2 and gnutls.</p>

<p>Ncdc is entirely written in C and available under a liberal MIT license.</p>

